@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mhjnra(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v2 + 0.96) - v1) - wp.sin(wp.exp(v1 + 0.45)))
    v1 = (wp.cos(0.85) * tmp)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.cos(v0 + 0.07)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.46)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.88)))
    data[tid] = v0
